profile:
At Honest D Plumbing, our goal is to 'exceed' customer expectations by providing affordable, top quality workmanship and excellent, friendly, courteous, professional and clean plumbing service each and every time.

Fully qualified, licensed and insured Plumber with over 10 years experience.  Company van ready to go to work for you.

Honest D deals with top quality suppliers right here in Ottawa to ensure you are getting high quality fixtures and products or maybe you prefer to buy your own.

Proud to serve the Ottawa area and surrounding Communities. 

 

Whether you are renovating your existing space, building a new home/space, getting your home ready to sell, want to fix the one you are moving into, or maybe you just need maintenance on your existing products to ensure you won't run into problems in the future, give 'Honest D' a call.
